_______________________________________________________________________________
"Create Image"   
        Using this power, the psionicist can trick others into
        perceiving something that is not in fact present.  This
        image can be of anything the psionicist can imagine, and
        can be colored white, yellow, red, or green to imitate
        items, coins, monsters, or weapons and armor,
        respectively.  The duration of the image is dependent
        on guild level.
 
SP Cost:  20	Guild Level:  4	  Potential Points:  1
 
Command:  create <whatever>
